Recipe
Pav Bhaji

Boil the vegetables.
smash the vegetables.
Take ginger,garlic grind it and make a paste.
Take a pan and add 2 tablespoon oil.
Add cumin seeds and Onion let the onion be in a brown colour.
Add smashed vegetable and add Tomatoes.
know,add the pav bhaji masala,Turmeric powder.
Add Red Chilli powder,butter and salt as per your taste.
put the lid on the pan and let it cook for 10 minutes.
Add butter on another pan and put pav on the pan andlet it bake for 10-12 seconds.
Add corriander leaves on bhaji and stir it for 12-14 seconds.
And pav bhaji is ready to serve.
